values: just got home from church and austin you are a dork, love! but thats ok b-cuz the sun will come out tomorrow!! yes, austin was mean to me today, he wouldnt give me a hug? and 4 real... its just a hug, would it kill him? aaron tried to break my arm off hahaha! he is a beautiful person indeed! but anyway... now that sarah anna, sarah grace, aaron, and austin are gone...i'm bored. i really want to go see willy wonka and the chocolate factory...every1 says its awesome! i'm supposed to see it wednesday but its sunday......3 days seems so long now. i mean 4 real its summer, i'm supposed to be having fun right? school starts in about 2 weeks now, so summer is drawing to a close already. but sadly i would have to say that for onece...i'm happy about going back to school. i know its weird but i think this year will be fun. with my cheerleading, girls show choir, and musical theatre..... i cant wait! not to mention the school dances. ive never been to one before so i'm exited! i hope i have a date because i already have a dress! its so pretty too, austin wants to see it hahaha! he is a total dork but i love him anyway! (did u see that one love? haha!) it goes to the floor and its a strappless turquoise dress... i absolutly love it! hopefully its going to be for homecoming because i still have to buy one for sweet 16 too! i doubt that i'll be going to prom though, but thats ok i still have 4 years! yeah rock it out and live it up!

i went shopping after church today. it was a lot of fun. we went to dothan but we should have gone to destin or tallahassee.  my friend broke his leg the other day and he had a tumor in it, so i'm stressed out right now. but anyway, i'm going to make this short so i can go talk to some ppl on aim. 

P.S. IF U KNOW ANDREW PLEASE PRAY FOR HIM NOW! THANX SO MUCH!

today was fun, went to my lake house and spent the day with mackenzie on the jet ski. got a darker tan too teehee! havnt seen mackenzie in a long time so we had a lot of fun. but yeah i'm watching the best movie ever... starring johnny depp and orlando bloom...pirates of the carribbean! a sequel is coming soon and it better be good! but for now... i'm going to finish up the movie and talk on aim for a while so this is short and sweet... like me! hehe!

i'm really really bored, i guess this is the blah time of day. i really want to call someone and go see a movie or something but sarah is at camp and theres nothing intresting playing anyways! i tried putting some pictures or icons on here but i cant figure it out. and by the way those of you that have summer gym classes with me... only one more week! yeah! at least they have the blacklights now... i guess thats a plus! and if your on the mhs jv cheerleading squad with me then someone please help me wth those cheers we had to memorize over july, since we had no practices this month i'm kinda blanked out! and another thing about that... when are we learning the pep rally dances? lol, typical me. show chior this year is going to be fun , along with musical theatre, but the new high school is so much better than the old one, despite the fact that its huge and i will be lost every moment that i spend in it! and for anyone who can answer this... whats up with the green? our school colors are purple gold and white, why is our school green? this confuses me...well anyway, i guess i'm gonna go find something else to do now, maybe shopping, sounds good!

P.S. sorry if this entry is really random, but i'm bored so i have an excuse this time!

i'm really bored right now, today was fun, hung out with my friends a lot. i found out that i suck at bowling... lol! but thats ok! i'm not that great at skateboarding either, but hey i just learned so i guess its fine for now. we go back to school on august 8th... fun. i'll be a freshman this year and my brother is going to be a junior so this should be intresting... lol! but my major concern is homecoming... i really want to have a date to the dance. my friends think that just because i'm a jv cheerleader i'll have a date, but i dont think that it works that way. but if i dont i guess i'll just go with my friends and have fun anyway! my friends are awesome so i wouldnt mind... but having a date would be better, depending on who he is of course. hes got to be hot thats a must! crap, just broke a nail...l8r!
me and my brother got in a wreck today, wasnt bad though, kinda scary. but...  really, nothing much happened today, so i really dont have much to write about! teehee
